Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:08.72,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There you go, making that face again,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:12.60,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k43}ku{\k32}chi{\k53}bi{\k20}ru{\k0} {\k25}ka{\k65}mi{\k36}shi{\k49}me{\k65}te{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:12.60,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}biting onto your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:18.54,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k6}{\k49}yo{\k21}wa{\k76}sa{\k0} {\k28}wo{\k0} {\k72}ka{\k23}ku{\k74}shi{\k34}te{\k45}ru{\k0} {\k25}ke{\k141}do{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:18.54,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're hiding your weak side,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:24.44,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k70}so{\k21}no{\k0} {\k80}hi{\k24}to{\k73}mi{\k0} {\k25}no{\k0} {\k51}o{\k69}ku{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:24.44,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but deep in those eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:28.39,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k46}u{\k29}zu{\k75}ku{\k32}ma{\k67}ru{\k0} {\k25}ki{\k46}mi{\k0} {\k75}ga{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:28.39,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can see you cowering.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:34.43,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k50}ho{\k27}n{\k71}to{\k0} {\k26}no{\k0} {\k71}ko{\k30}ko{\k49}ro{\k0} {\k48}na{\k232}ra{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:34.43,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you had a true heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.58,0:00:39.84,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k14}{\k30}o{\k25}mo{\k20}t{\k51}te,{\k0} {\k38}na{\k15}i{\k38}te,{\k0} {\k13}hi{\k18}to{\k0} {\k21}yo{\k9}n{\k39}de,{\k0} {\k14}fu{\k33}wa{\k10}n{\k37}de{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.58,0:00:39.84,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you would care, cry, call for someone and worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:43.48,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k39}na{\k19}n{\k33}de{\k0} {\k17}i{\k33}ta{\k14}i{\k0} {\k49}no{\k0} {\k41}mo{\k14}t{\k31}te{\k14}n{\k57}da{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:43.48,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you holding onto the pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:50.23,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k16}{\k24}bo{\k50}ku{\k0} {\k39}ni{\k0} {\k45}so{\k18}t{\k46}to{\k0} {\k39}a{\k9}zu{\k49}ke{\k50}te{\k0} {\k290}yo{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:50.23,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Share some of it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:55.78,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k16}{\k35}su{\k45}gu{\k0} {\k25}ja{\k0} {\k30}mu{\k48}ri{\k0} {\k19}to{\k0} {\k29}o{\k30}mo{\k17}u{\k0} {\k25}no{\k0} {\k25}na{\k52}ra{\k55}ba{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:55.78,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you don't think it's possible right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:59.18,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k9}{\k24}su{\k25}ko{\k29}shi{\k0} {\k49}zu{\k26}tsu{\k0} {\k30}de{\k0} {\k20}i{\k128}i{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:59.18,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you can do it slowly, bit by bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:03.28,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k48}tsu{\k12}ba{\k35}sa{\k0} {\k24}no{\k0} {\k29}na{\k19}i{\k0} {\k28}bo{\k22}ku{\k48}ra{\k0} {\k39}ki{\k13}t{\k45}to{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:03.28,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We don't have wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:07.08,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k31}to{\k23}be{\k33}na{\k16}i{\k0} {\k23}to{\k24}ki{\k0} {\k16}mi{\k31}tsu{\k23}ke{\k54}te{\k26}ru{\k0} {\k25}da{\k55}ke{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:07.08,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but I'm sure we're only finding times that we can't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:11.58,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k15}{\k28}ko{\k48}e{\k0} {\k24}no{\k0} {\k22}ka{\k55}gi{\k21}ri{\k0} {\k30}ki{\k44}mi{\k0} {\k24}wo{\k0} {\k29}yo{\k43}bu{\k0} {\k67}yo{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:11.58,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll call for you to the limits of my voice
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:15.05,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k9}{\k24}ma{\k26}yo{\k26}wa{\k23}na{\k18}i{\k0} {\k30}yo{\k28}u{\k0} {\k163}ni{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:15.05,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so that you won't get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:18.85,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k28}fu{\k28}wa{\k20}ri{\k0} {\k24}ko{\k50}ko{\k28}ro{\k0} {\k21}ma{\k50}i{\k23}a{\k28}ga{\k25}re{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:18.85,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Soar up to the sky with your gentle heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:26.84,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k17}{\k28}a{\k21}no{\k0} {\k45}ka{\k38}ze{\k0} {\k20}ni{\k0} {\k26}no{\k46}se{\k95}te{\k0} {\k13}i{\k5}s{\k27}se{\k7}i{\k0} {\k10}e{\k26}ro{\k372}se{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:26.84,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ride on that wind, and get it all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:40.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was small, I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:46.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,sometimes see strange things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:49.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A kappa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:54.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:56.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:16.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:43.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-kun, don't forget, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:44.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:47.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,"Eh?" I'm talking about tonight's test of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:52.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really feel up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you to come because we didn't have enough people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:58.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you being a bit anti-social?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:01.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it that you have something more important to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:03.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:05.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The old school building is going to be demolished next week,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:08.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,so this year's test of courage will be the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you come, since we'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:19.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,During the dark nights of summer, there are more lurking Youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be okay if I do the test of courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:25.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:35.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you follow me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:38.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it looks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:40.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You need me as a bodyguard for times like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:46.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that cat just make a strange noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:49.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, you're probably just imagining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:50.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:54.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't talk in front of anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:57.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real handful, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:58.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:00.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I got it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:09.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The instructions are to go in pairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:12.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,write your names on the wall at the end of the second floor hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and then come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:17.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't set up people to scare you, so you can be scared safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:19.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll decide the pairings through a lottery
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:23.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,ranging from one to twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:25.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Everyone draw a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:37.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a story about this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:42.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, there was a god of fortune who loved humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:45.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and he would appear as a child to play among the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:46.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:53.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a greedy merchant who wanted more riches,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:56.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and he locked him up in his cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:05:00.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, the merchant would reap huge profits because of the fortune power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:05.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the dark cellar, the God of Youth mourned and mourned,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,grew to resent people,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:11.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and eventually became an evil spectre.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:15.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The merchant's house became bankrupt,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:19.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and eventually this school building was erected on this spot of bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:25.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The God of Youth lamented that he became an abominable Ayakashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:29.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and even now he wanders this place, or so they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:33.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:36.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No real reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:44.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So everyone drew one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:46.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then show your lots on the count of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:47.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We're missing one lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There were twenty numbers, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:55.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We have one person too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:57.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just someone who came and didn't bother to sign up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The committee did this on purpose, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:03.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:05.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe someone took two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:09.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:13.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the thing Sasada talked about earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if he's here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:19.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,then he must be strong enough that even I can't sense him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:24.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:26.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:31.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be the Book of Friends' fault, can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:43.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We should've been paired up with girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:45.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:52.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's run-down, but it kind of makes you feel sad that it's going to be demolished.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:53.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't seen anyone else yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:06:59.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, now that you mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way were we supposed to go, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:20.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:28.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the password?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:46.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:56.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you've awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:07:59.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have I seen that face before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:01.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:07.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only have you defiled me, but now you're stealing my home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:15.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,People are such selfish beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:18.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:19.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:20.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:26.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:27.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:30.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Nishimura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:45.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you see my partner, Kitamoto-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I took my eyes off of him for a second, and then we got separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:53.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The first group still hasn't returned either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:55.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:56.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:59.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was taken away by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:04.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Who were you calling out to earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:09.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Natsume-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:11.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,you can see them, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:16.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You do strange things sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're startled when there's nothing there,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:22.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and talk when there's no one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:29.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they things not of this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:31.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:33.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep it a secret from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:42.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what is it? You can see them, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:50.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanko-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:55.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So she wasn't an Ayakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:56.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:20.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like there's a barrier around the entire school building and we can't get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:24.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you go and see if there's a way out somewhere, sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:25.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:26.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What a slave driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:37.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This form will be more convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:47.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like a dodgeball came flying at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:52.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:57.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She's part of the dodgeball club,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:00.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and came to get her ball that got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:04.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So we had a dodgeball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:07.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll go take a look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:09.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look for a way out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,so relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:15.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed pretty conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:17.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's the captain, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:23.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a person! A person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So, people are still around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:27.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We must report this to Shigure-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:29.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you low-level punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:32.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Our eyes met!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:35.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:39.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:43.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a district event, so I participated in a test of courage here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:47.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I cried and ran around the school building,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:52.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and when I got home, I realized I had lost something precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:55.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,In a panic, I went back to the school to search for it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:01.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared and disheartened,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't find it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:05.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:07.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been doing this entire time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:24.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I dropped my charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:26.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:29.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it quickly and leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:36.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:39.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,, I didn't give up and continued to look for it for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And just when I was about to give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:45.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:50.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:52.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:57.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:12:59.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I had almost given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:02.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a memento from my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:05.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that stick, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:11.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,An impure being such as myself cannot touch anything that is pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're done now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:14.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Impure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:17.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:18.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:23.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,With the way he talked and his presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:28.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered if he was a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:33.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So I looked it up and learned the story about the God of Youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:37.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I also learned that "impure" meant "defiled."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:40.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I would come here every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:43.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to thank him, and so called for him to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:46.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And I wanted to say, "You're not impure!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:50.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, he never showed himself to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:57.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, if you can see things like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:59.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is going to be demolished,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:03.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought that this was my last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:09.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for saying it like that earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:10.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:15.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You really can't see them, Natsume-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:25.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No one came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:43.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:47.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:50.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:52.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanko-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:57.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,His servants are low-level, but he's a surprisingly big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,His name seems to be in the Book of Friends as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:02.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ayakashi's name is Shigure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Shigure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a real bother, so let's leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:12.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a powerful barrier, but I can manage to break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:14.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:17.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What about everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:19.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:25.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nightmares about your childhood, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:32.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, we can't leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:35.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want do things that I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:42.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:45.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:48.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:50.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:51.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:58.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The underlings are gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:01.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on the roof, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:02.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:04.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:04.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's "he?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:06.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:08.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:14.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Sasada?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:16.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,To see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:17.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on the roof, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:19.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:20.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:26.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell him how precious this charm is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:29.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and how happy I was that he found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:33.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:39.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Sasada somewhere safe, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:42.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:43.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Make him stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return his name and persuade him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:46.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Na...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:48.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:24.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I was wondering where you had gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:26.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and now you've come to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:30.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:32.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:37.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They turned me into this abominable Ayakashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:39.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,entered this place as if to make fun of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:42.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and even tried to steal my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:44.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never return them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:48.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see your parents crying and mourning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:51.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a girl who wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:54.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The other girl left inside the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:57.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:00.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't understand, Natsume-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:05.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Reiko's relative, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:08.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You could have just used the Book of Friends to make me obey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:09.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:13.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that makes things easier. I will return your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:15.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need liberation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer need that defiled name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:32.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have just burnt it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:54.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Shigure-sama, I return your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:59.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A name that belongs to a kind being who helped support a girl's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:21.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That noisy one has come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:25.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to thank you! I just have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:28.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to drive her out quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:31.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and so I helped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:36.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Day after day,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:38.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and never giving up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:40.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bizarre being.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:44.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If an impure being such as myself touched her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:47.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Would I really defile her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:51.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Just once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:55.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, just by meeting her once...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:57.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:58.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't come again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:05.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:08.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired from being unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:14.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Shigure-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:15.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasada said...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:18.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that you're not impure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:20.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She said you saved her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:24.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to believe in a person's words,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:26.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but at least believe in Sasada's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:27.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:29.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:37.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:42.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Only you and Reiko did not fear me for being impure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:57.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:08.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:08.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:14.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-kun, last night, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:18.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:21.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was on the roof and sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:26.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:37.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasada, the truth is that for a moment, I saw Shigure-sama touch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:41.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw your hearts trying to connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:45.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you felt anything.
